CB Giveaway is here! 
During this Covid19, WHO encouraged us to wash our hands often with soap and water. 
So let's do it! Wash hands leh!

We will be doing a 20 sets (1 Natural Bar soap & 1 Bathenet) giveaway to our followers on our Facebook & IG. 
3 simple steps:
1) Like and share this post to public (IG may share in your story) 
2) Follow our social media (If you follow both IG and FB you will stand double chance) 
3) Comment 'I want CB giveaway'

Draw date: 16 May 2020
We will pack and mail out on 18 May 2020 via Singpost (Singapore only)
